# ŌöĆŌöĆ Command: CONNECT ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
# Launches an SSH session directly. Clears the screen beforehand so the
# connection gets a clean terminal, then redraws the banner on return.

cmd_connect() {
    _use_agent=0; _use_sshpass=0; _alias=""
    while [ "$#" -gt 0 ]; do
        case "$1" in
            --agent)   _use_agent=1 ;;
            --sshpass) _use_sshpass=1 ;;
            *)         _alias="$1" ;;
        esac
        shift
    done
    [ -z "$_alias" ] && die "Usage: termio connect <alias> [--agent] [--sshpass]"
    alias_exists "$_alias" || die "Alias \"$_alias\" not found."

    # Apply per-alias preferences (flags override)
    [ "$(pref_get "auto_agent_$_alias")" = "yes" ] && _use_agent=1
    _stored_pw=$(pref_get "sshpass_$_alias")
    [ -n "$_stored_pw" ] && [ "$_use_sshpass" -eq 0 ] && _use_sshpass=2

    _host=$(get_field "$_alias" "HostName")
    _user=$(get_field "$_alias" "User")
    _port=$(get_field "$_alias" "Port"); [ -z "$_port" ] && _port="22"

    printf '\n'
    info "Connecting to ${C_BOLD}$_alias${C_RESET} (${_user}@${_host}:${_port})"
    printf "  Press ${C_BOLD}Ctrl+D${C_RESET} or type ${C_BOLD}exit${C_RESET} to return to termio.\n\n"
    pref_set "last_connect_${_alias}" "$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')"

    # Auto-add key to agent if requested
    if [ "$_use_agent" -eq 1 ]; then
        _akey=$(get_field "$_alias" "IdentityFile")
        if [ -n "$_akey" ] && [ -f "$_akey" ] && command -v ssh-add >/dev/null 2>&1; then
            ssh-add "$_akey" 2>/dev/null && vlog "Key auto-added to agent for $_alias"
        fi
    fi

    sleep 0.4
    clear 2>/dev/null || printf '\033[2J\033[H'

    set +e
    if [ "$_use_sshpass" -eq 1 ]; then
        command -v sshpass >/dev/null 2>&1 || { warn "sshpass not installed."; set -e; return 1; }
        printf 'SSH password for %s@%s: ' "$_user" "$_host"
        stty -echo 2>/dev/null; IFS= read -r _sp; stty echo 2>/dev/null; printf '\n'
        SSHPASS="$_sp" sshpass -e ssh -F "$CONFIG_FILE" "$_alias"
        _ssh_exit=$?
        unset _sp SSHPASS
    elif [ "$_use_sshpass" -eq 2 ]; then
        command -v sshpass >/dev/null 2>&1 || { warn "sshpass not installed."; set -e; return 1; }
        _sp=$(printf '%s' "$_stored_pw" | base64 -d 2>/dev/null)
        unset _stored_pw
        SSHPASS="$_sp" sshpass -e ssh -F "$CONFIG_FILE" "$_alias"
        _ssh_exit=$?
        unset _sp SSHPASS
    else
        ssh -F "$CONFIG_FILE" "$_alias"
        _ssh_exit=$?
    fi
    set -e

    clear 2>/dev/null || printf '\033[2J\033[H'

    if [ "$_ssh_exit" -ne 0 ] && [ "$_ssh_exit" -ne 130 ]; then
        warn "SSH exited with code $_ssh_exit"
    fi
    unset _stored_pw _use_agent _use_sshpass
}

# ŌöĆŌöĆ RUN ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ

cmd_run() {
    _alias="$1"; shift
    _cmd="$*"
    [ -z "$_alias" ] && die "Usage: termio run <alias> <command>"
    [ -z "$_cmd"   ] && die "Usage: termio run <alias> <command>"
    alias_exists "$_alias" || die "Alias \"$_alias\" not found."
    _host=$(get_field "$_alias" "HostName")
    _user=$(get_field "$_alias" "User")
    _port=$(get_field "$_alias" "Port"); [ -z "$_port" ] && _port="22"
    printf '\n'
    info "Running on ${C_BOLD}$_alias${C_RESET} (${_user}@${_host}:${_port})"
    printf "  ${C_BOLD}Command:${C_RESET} ${C_DIM}%s${C_RESET}\n\n" "$_cmd"
    set +e
    ssh -F "$CONFIG_FILE" \
        -o BatchMode=yes \
        -o ConnectTimeout=10 \
        -o StrictHostKeyChecking=accept-new \
        "$_alias" "$_cmd"
    _rc=$?
    set -e
    printf '\n'
    [ "$_rc" -eq 0 ] && success "Done." || warn "Command exited with code $_rc"
    printf '\n'
}

# ŌöĆŌöĆ COPY ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ

cmd_copy() {
    _src="${1:-}"; _dst="${2:-}"
    { [ -z "$_src" ] || [ -z "$_dst" ]; } && \
        die "Usage: termio copy <alias>:/remote/path /local/path\n       termio copy /local/path <alias>:/remote/path"
    command -v scp >/dev/null 2>&1 || die "scp not found ŌĆö install openssh-client"
    _alias=""
    case "$_src" in *:*) _alias="${_src%%:*}" ;; esac
    case "$_dst" in
        *:*) [ -z "$_alias" ] && _alias="${_dst%%:*}" ;;
    esac
    [ -z "$_alias" ] && die "One path must be in <alias>:/path format (e.g. myserver:/etc/hosts)"
    alias_exists "$_alias" || die "Alias \"$_alias\" not found."
    _host=$(get_field "$_alias" "HostName")
    _user=$(get_field "$_alias" "User")
    printf '\n'
    info "Copying:  ${C_BOLD}$_src${C_RESET}  ŌåÆ  ${C_BOLD}$_dst${C_RESET}"
    printf "  (via %s@%s using ~/.ssh/config)\n\n" "$_user" "$_host"
    set +e
    scp -F "$CONFIG_FILE" -r "$_src" "$_dst"
    _rc=$?
    set -e
    printf '\n'
    [ "$_rc" -eq 0 ] && success "Copy complete." || warn "scp exited with code $_rc"
    printf '\n'
}

# ŌöĆŌöĆ STATUS DASHBOARD ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ

cmd_status() {
    _aliases=$(list_aliases)
    if [ -z "$_aliases" ]; then
        printf '\n  No aliases configured. Add one with: termio add\n\n'; return 0
    fi
    _timeout=8
    _tmpdir=$(mktemp -d 2>/dev/null || mktemp -d -t termio)
    _total=$(printf '%s\n' "$_aliases" | grep -c .)

    # Launch parallel SSH probes with ms latency measurement
    while IFS= read -r _a; do
        [ -z "$_a" ] && continue
        (
            _ts=$(date +%s%3N 2>/dev/null || printf '%s000' "$(date +%s)")
            if ssh -F "$CONFIG_FILE" \
                   -o BatchMode=yes \
                   -o ConnectTimeout="$_timeout" \
                   -o StrictHostKeyChecking=accept-new \
                   "$_a" true 2>/dev/null; then
                _te=$(date +%s%3N 2>/dev/null || printf '%s000' "$(date +%s)")
                printf 'ok:%d' "$(( _te - _ts ))" > "$_tmpdir/$_a"
            else
                printf 'fail' > "$_tmpdir/$_a"
            fi
        ) &
    done <<_EOST
$(printf '%s\n' "$_aliases")
_EOST

    # Spinner while probes run
    printf '\n'
    _spin_i=0
    while true; do
        _done=$(ls "$_tmpdir" 2>/dev/null | wc -l)
        [ "$_done" -ge "$_total" ] && break
        case $(( _spin_i % 10 )) in
            0) _sc='ŌĀŗ' ;; 1) _sc='ŌĀÖ' ;; 2) _sc='ŌĀ╣' ;; 3) _sc='ŌĀĖ' ;; 4) _sc='ŌĀ╝' ;;
            5) _sc='ŌĀ┤' ;; 6) _sc='ŌĀ”' ;; 7) _sc='ŌĀ¦' ;; 8) _sc='ŌĀć' ;; 9) _sc='ŌĀÅ' ;;
        esac
        printf '\r  %s  Probing %d / %d aliases...' "$_sc" "$_done" "$_total"
        sleep 0.1
        _spin_i=$(( _spin_i + 1 ))
    done
    printf '\r%60s\r' ''
    wait

    # Boxed results table ŌĆö col widths: alias(18) host(22) status(15) last(13)
    _SW1=20; _SW2=24; _SW3=17; _SW4=15
    _ls_hline "  Ōöī" "Ōö¼" "ŌöÉ" "$_SW1" "$_SW2" "$_SW3" "$_SW4"
    printf "  Ōöé ${C_BOLD}${C_LBLUE}%-18s${C_RESET} Ōöé ${C_BOLD}${C_LBLUE}%-22s${C_RESET} Ōöé ${C_BOLD}${C_LBLUE}%-15s${C_RESET} Ōöé ${C_BOLD}${C_LBLUE}%-13s${C_RESET} Ōöé\n" \
        "ALIAS" "HOSTNAME" "STATUS" "LAST SEEN"
    _ls_hline "  Ōö£" "Ōö╝" "Ōöż" "$_SW1" "$_SW2" "$_SW3" "$_SW4"

    while IFS= read -r _a; do
        [ -z "$_a" ] && continue
        _h=$(get_field "$_a" "HostName")
        _last=$(pref_get "last_connect_$_a")
        _relts=$(_rel_time "$_last")
        _res=""
        [ -f "$_tmpdir/$_a" ] && _res=$(cat "$_tmpdir/$_a")
        case "$_res" in
            ok:*)
                _ms=${_res#ok:}
                if   [ "$_ms" -lt 50  ]; then _lat_col="$C_GREEN"
                elif [ "$_ms" -lt 200 ]; then _lat_col="$C_YELLOW"
                else                          _lat_col="$C_RED"; fi
                _status_str=$(printf "${C_GREEN}Ō£ö up${C_RESET}  ${_lat_col}%dms${C_RESET}" "$_ms")
                ;;
            *)
                _status_str="${C_RED}Ō£ś unreachable${C_RESET}"
                ;;
        esac
        printf "  Ōöé ${C_BOLD}%-18.18s${C_RESET} Ōöé %-22.22s Ōöé %-15b Ōöé ${C_DIM}%-13.13s${C_RESET} Ōöé\n" \
            "$_a" "$_h" "$_status_str" "$_relts"
    done <<_EOST2
$(printf '%s\n' "$_aliases")
_EOST2

    _ls_hline "  Ōöö" "Ōö┤" "Ōöś" "$_SW1" "$_SW2" "$_SW3" "$_SW4"
    rm -rf "$_tmpdir"
    printf '\n'
}

