wt_help() {
    _ht=$(cat <<'HELPEOF'
MENU ITEMS

  connect   Open an SSH session to a saved alias.

  add       Guided wizard ŌĆö alias name, host, user, port, note,
            optional jump/bastion host, and advanced SSH options.
            Generates a unique ed25519 key and copies it to the
